  [ Salvatore Bonaccorso ]
  * d/p/CVE-2021-3560.patch:
    Fix local privilege escalation involving
    polkit_system_bus_name_get_creds_sync() (CVE-2021-3560)
    (Closes: #989429)

 -- Simon McVittie <smcv@debian.org>  Thu, 03 Jun 2021 17:06:34 +0100

